      <ul id="tribute-info">
        <li>1991 - Created the Linux kernal and the version control system Git</li>
        <li>2004 - Named one of the "100 Most Influential People in the World" by Time Magazine</li>
        <li>2010 - Recieved an honorary doctorate from the University of Helsinki</li>
        <li>2010 - Recieved the 2010 Millennium Technology Prize</li>
        <li>2013 - Inducted into the Internet Hall of Fame for his contribuition to the development of the Linux kernel and the creation of Git</li>


        </ul>
